      <title>德国财长肖尔茨将与印度总理莫迪会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-25/germany-s-scholz-in-india-to-meet-with-modi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨正在印度进行为期三天的访问，随行的还有由部长和高管组成的大型代表团，他希望与印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪建立战略伙伴关系。彭博社的苏迪·兰詹·森 (Sudhi Ranjan Sen) 分析了肖尔茨此行的意义以及他与莫迪会晤的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-25/germany-s-scholz-in-india-to-meet-with-modi</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 07:16:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国传将起诉法国巴黎银行非法卖空</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/korea-is-said-to-indict-bnp-paribas-for-illegal-short-selling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，韩国检察机关已起诉法国巴黎银行（BNP Paribas SA）涉嫌违反卖空规定，这是韩国打击此类交易的最新进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/korea-is-said-to-indict-bnp-paribas-for-illegal-short-selling</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 06:43:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士河向债权人寻求 30 亿英镑紧急现金需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/thames-water-unveils-plan-to-raise-3-billion-from-creditors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务有限公司周五公布了一项提案，寻求从债权人那里筹集高达 30 亿英镑（39 亿美元）的资金，以争取更多时间，避免在明年初进入特别托管阶段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/thames-water-unveils-plan-to-raise-3-billion-from-creditors</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 06:27:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚先令走强，加查瓜遭弹劾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-25/kenya-schilling-strengthens-gachagua-impeached-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来最严重的政治动荡并没有影响肯尼亚表现最好的货币以及不断上涨的债券和股票市场，因为投资者关注的是经济改善和健康的资本流入。与此同时，肯尼亚副总统里加蒂·加查瓜因滥用权力和腐败而被弹劾。彭博新闻社的 Ondiro Oganga 与 Jennifer Zabasajja 就中东和非洲视野进行了讨论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-25/kenya-schilling-strengthens-gachagua-impeached-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 05:39:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>增长前景恶化，印度中型股进入调整期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/india-mid-cap-stocks-head-for-correction-as-growth-outlook-sours</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者对盈利增长放缓和估值过高的担忧日益增加，中型股的强劲上涨即将进入回调区域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/india-mid-cap-stocks-head-for-correction-as-growth-outlook-sours</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 05:39:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赛诺菲利润因早期疫苗销售和 Dupixent 增长而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/sanofi-reports-higher-profit-lifted-by-early-sales-of-vaccines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赛诺菲的利润因季节性疫苗的需求和其重磅皮肤和哮喘治疗药物 Dupixent 的进一步增长而增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/sanofi-reports-higher-profit-lifted-by-early-sales-of-vaccines</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 05:32:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>行业组织称中国将在 2030 年左右达到铜产量峰值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/china-s-copper-demand-will-peak-by-2030-says-industry-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位政府背景的研究人员表示，中国的铜需求将在本世纪末达到峰值，这可能与对铜前景的乐观看法形成鲜明对比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/china-s-copper-demand-will-peak-by-2030-says-industry-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 05:31:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者等待回购结果，韩国锌价进一步上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/korea-zinc-surges-even-higher-as-investors-await-buyback-result</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国锌业公司 (Korea Zinc Co.) 股价周五上涨，前一天上涨了 30%，因为市场正在等待董事长崔润范 (Choi Yun-beom) 推出的股票回购计划的结果，该计划旨在抵御 125 亿美元的收购要约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/korea-zinc-surges-even-higher-as-investors-await-buyback-result</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 00:52:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>名厨有望在韩国 IPO 中获利 2.15 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/culinary-class-wars-judge-to-boost-korea-s-ipo-market-with-61-million-listing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位凭借 Netflix 热门节目而出名的厨师帮助提振了韩国陷入困境的 IPO 市场，他的连锁餐厅上市，其所持股份的估值为 2.15 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/culinary-class-wars-judge-to-boost-korea-s-ipo-market-with-61-million-listing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 00:14:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：收益率飙升后标普 500 指数有望周度下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔 500 指数期货几乎没有变化，由于借贷成本上升打击了投资者情绪，该指数将出现七周以来的首次周线下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 22:30:16 GMT</pubDate>
